TikTok influencer EDA project

Initial upload of the full exploratory data analysis on the top 1000 
TikTok influencers dataset (Kaggle). Includes:

R Markdown source (.Rmd) covering all 13 analysis phases: data 
  wrangling, web scraping via rvest, string processing, and 
  ggplot2 visualizations
Rendered HTML report with final 25-page writeup and ten deliverables
README with project overview, dataset source, and methodology summary

Project completed as part of coursework; demonstrates data cleaning, 
feature engineering, and exploratory statistics in R.
